THE FIRM

With a global reputation for leadership and vision, Electrum Partners is an advisory services firm specializing in medical and recreational cannabis and ancillary businesses, founded by Leslie Bocskor, former investment banker known for success, leadership and disruption in emerging markets, technologies and finance.  The experienced senior leadership team takes great pride in engineering the underpinnings of successful business entries and exits across the full spectrum of cannabis business verticals, and helping to develop policy and regulatory frameworks with an acute understanding and knowledge of regulatory complexities.









WHAT WE DO

We partner with private and public companies, policy-makers, governments, entrepreneurs and investors looking for an edge to improve and maximize shareholder value and liquidity, as well as companies that are looking to make the private-to-public transition.  We know that cannabis is not a single industry but dozens of sub-industries, each with its own barriers-to-entry, capital requirements, unique market traits, and paths to success. As we help bring your ideas to fruition, we draw upon our ability to identify opportunities and create wins. You can count on Electrum Partners to help grow your business’ value and footprint, assisting you to navigate through markets where tumultuous dynamics are at work.









HOW WE DO IT

Brutal honesty.   Subject mastery.   Purpose.We are driven to help companies become winners in a crowded landscape by putting experienced leaders into your value chain to help shape your future success.  We will help you develop strategies from a competitive context, bringing powerful solutions for growth, added value, and the knowledge to forge a path forward (or the awareness and confidence to pivot away). We respect big ideas and worship attention to detail, diligence, expertise and planning, but also thrive on seizing opportunity, and gracefully navigating hurdles when the moment calls.   We value questions as much as answers, consider teamwork the highest calling, and believe wisdom is best served with a side of humility and humanity.  We help turn winners into leaders and we turn them loose.









