The Electrum Group LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 11:58 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of The Electrum Group LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
The Electrum Group LLC is a privately owned investment manager. It invests in public equity markets and in private companies. The firm primarily invests in natural resources sector with a focus on precious metals resources and hydrocarbons. It employs fundamental analysis to create its portfolio. The Electrum Group LLC was founded in 2011 and is based in New York, New York with additional office in Denver, Colorado.


535 Madison Avenue, 11th FloorNew York, NY 10022United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: 646-365-1600








